        Clause 18 [<span class="italic">Publicising reports: health care providers</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0668P0-04454'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0668P0_20050125_GCR_184' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 34 not moved.</span>]
