        Clause 24 [<span class="italic">Consultation and co-operation with other ombudsmen</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0668P0-04484'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0668P0_20050125_GCR_214' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
